  "text": ". Moreover, methods for examining single-molecule protein-binding sites are slowly but steadily improving [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . What is clear is that the field needs to advance beyond ensemble methods if we are ever to gain a complete understanding of origin function.",
